- Uh...
- Doesn't matter.

75
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,680
- Huh?
- Yes.

76
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,600
- I'll go.
- Mm.

77
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,600
- Awesome!
- Whoa!

78
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:45,960
Uh.

79
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,000
Am I...

80
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:53,120
