81
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,180
Just go to sleep.

82
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,080
Hey.

83
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,200
Hm?

84
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,040
So we're...

85
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:18,960
friends?

86
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,160
Don't know.

87
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,140
But...

88
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,640
there's no other word for it.

89
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,540
So probably, yeah.

90
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:35,080
Minase.

91
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,040
Thank you for inviting me.

92
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,140
Good night.

93
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,400
Good night.

94
