Absolutely not.

102
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:25,920
What?

103
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,220
Hm? What's going on?

104
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,000
Nothing.

105
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,220
Mm.

106
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:38,360
- Then let's choose the leader.
- Are you interested?

107
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,120
Uh, just a moment.

108
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,220
Done.

109
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,160
(What was that today? Don't do that.)

110
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,340
(Sorry, I was just happy
we were in the same group.)

111
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,280
(Let's start tomorrow.)

112
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,320
(Let's start tomorrow.)

113
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,580
(Don't mess with me in public.)

114
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:21,280
(We're in the same group.
Would be strange to avoid that.)

115
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:23,080
(Do whatever you want.)

116
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,320
Jeez, that guy.

117
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:56,280
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

118
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:59,780
Hey, we're together, so who's Shiba with?

119
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:02,240
- He's with Mr. Wajima.
- Mr. Wajima, right?

120
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:04,900
Whoa, Mr. Fuji!

121
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:08,480
- Awesome.
- Wow, it's huge.

122
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:13,640
Hey, are you okay?

123
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:17,260
Mm, I got a lot of sleep on the bus
so I feel better now.

124
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:20,480
And I just walked around the first museum.

125
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,740
Well...

126
00:10:22,140 --> 00:10:23,100
Let's go.

127
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:31,020
You don't have to go hiking.

128
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,060
Your symptoms are getting worse.

129
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,380
You're right.

130
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,620
Going back alone?

131
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,680
Mm, I'll tell the teacher and go back.

132
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,540
Get lots of sleep.

133
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:50,340
From now on, focus. Especially you.

134
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:52,900
Thank you.

135
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:55,040
That's true.

136
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,100
- Fifteen maybe.
- Isn't that too much?

137
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:57,940
Well...

138
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:58,680
- Hey.
- Oh.

139
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:01,200
- Shiba, sit here.
- Oh, where's Minase?

140
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:04,720
Oh, he's sick so he's
staying in a separate room.

141
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:06,240
Is that so?

142
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:08,160
- Too bad.
- Mm.

143
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,360
Eh? What?

144
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,660
Looks like you have a fever.

145
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,500
Aren't you going to dinner?

146
00:11:26,140 --> 00:11:27,340
You weren't there.

147
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:31,000
I bought a lot of food. Let's eat.

148
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,060
What should we eat?

149
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:38,160
You really didn't need to come.

150
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:41,000
You're okay with it, but I'm not.

151
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:43,420
It's lonely sleeping
with a cold by yourself.

152
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:46,460
I'm used to being alone.

153
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,420
Ah, this one.

154
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,140
My mom...

155
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:56,600
She bought it for me whenever I got sick.

156
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:01,080
So let's eat that.

157
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,920
Unlike you to have a
cold on a day like this.

158
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:18,300
I studied with my window open yesterday.

159
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:20,360
Then I fell asleep.

160
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:24,060
You should've gone to bed early
the night before a field trip.

161
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:27,740
Something kept me up.

162
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,080
I see.

163
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:32,020
Excited about spending nights elsewhere?

164
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,120
Huh?

165
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:34,680
No.

166
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:38,060
I was frustrated
because of your strange messages.

167
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:41,720
Why were you frustrated?

168
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,800
Uh, you're gonna catch a cold.

169
00:12:58,260 --> 00:13:00,680
They say the cold goes away
if you infect other people.

170
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:04,300
That's not a treatment.

171
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:08,940
Then infect me.

172
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:12,680
Huh?

173
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,640
Infect me...

174
00:13:37,540 --> 00:13:38,940
just a little.

175
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,560
It's melted.

176
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:39,340
You're like a child.

177
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,420
Ah, made you laugh.

178
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:45,540
Probably delirious from the fever.

179
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:50,880
You should have a fever all the time then.

180
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:55,240
I'm going to sleep.

181
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,620
What?

182
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,020
Nothing.

183
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,700
I'll be right here.

184
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,320
Relax and go to sleep.

185
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,620
Oh, Shiba, Shiba,
Shiba. This is it, a heart.

186
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:42,840
Huh? It's nothing like a heart.

187
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:45,660
- Really?
- Yeah, but I need it.

188
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:46,540
There you go.

189
00:15:46,540 --> 00:15:49,080
- Is this one good?
- It's just that guy.

190
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:52,380
- Eh? It's creepy.
- I don't know.

191
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,980
That's cute.

192
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,980
No, I just picked it up by accident.

193
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,900
A souvenir for the girl you like?

194
00:16:07,780 --> 00:16:09,340
I told you there wasn't one.

195
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,400
Mm.

196
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:12,920
Hey, Shiba.

197
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,440
- Shiba.
- Hm?

198
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:15,760
How much money do you have?

199
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:19,920
- I'm off.
- Bye-bye!

200
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:21,000
Take care.

201
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:53,180
Were you looking at me?

202
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:57,140
Just happened to be next to you.

203
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:06,140
Hey.

204
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,180
Your hand...

205
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,160
It's cool, so it feels good.

206
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:35,680
Here.

207
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,860
For yesterday.

208
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,620
Eh? For me?

209
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:41,920
Mm.

210
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,640
I guess it's childish.

211
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,560
Not at all.

212
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:00,860
Very cute.

213
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,340
I like it.

214
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,660
That's good.

215
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:14,840
Thank you.

216
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:18,500
Mm.

217
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,100
Good night.

218
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,500
Good night.

