225
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:18,360
(Can you come out now?)

226
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:33,120
Sorry, it's nothing urgent.

227
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:35,300
It's okay.

228
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:37,940
I wanted to come outside anyway.

229
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,440
What happened?

230
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,420
Minase?

231
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:08,060
I may have to study abroad.

232
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:12,100
Eh?

233
00:21:14,660 --> 00:21:18,160
Looks like my parents
are getting a divorce.

234
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:22,480
I knew it would happen someday.

235
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:27,960
But it happens faster than I expected.

236
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,300
Don't worry.

237
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:43,200
If...

238
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:47,060
you're not okay,

239
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,760
you can always tell me.

240
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:58,040
The more I'm with you, the weaker I become.

241
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:06,540
But when I'm with you,

242
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:09,360
I'm stronger.

243
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:32,900
I really don't want to study abroad.

244
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:37,060
Mm.

245
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:39,800
Don't go.

246
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:44,180
It's like the boundary
between the sky and the sea

247
00:22:44,620 --> 00:22:46,220
that becomes blurry.

248
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:51,140
I hope the boundary between me and you

249
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:53,160
will fuse and disappear.

250
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,200
In that moment, I...

251
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:02,560
was imagining it like it was a dream.

